  "title": "Fleming Joins the Sith",
  "summary": "Aboard the Star Destroyer Predator, hidden in an asteroid field, ISB Sector Director Korynn Fleming and the former Commodore Lynae Cassius warily reunite, both having been brought into Darth Malign's secret Sith organization that serves Emperor Vadim. When their old animosity flares, Malign appears and silences their bickering, asserting his absolute authority before escorting them at blasterpoint to the ship's Sith meditation chamber. There, surrounded by sentient, poison-firing Sith dart flowers, Malign reveals his grand design: a hidden military complex being built beneath the ruined world of Cochran and a mission to plumb dead worlds for lost Sith secrets, using their combined expertise. Fleming, his loyalty to the Emperor absolute, swears himself to the order at once, while Lynae remains torn, confessing that the weight of blood already on her hands and a doubt planted by the Jedi Johanna stay her hand. Malign presses her to embrace her humanity and passion, granting her time to settle one last matter of the heart before giving her answer; he then dismisses them to meditate, leaving both free to roam the ship.",
